{"tid":378181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日打風 想同一位好心人講多謝","createTime":"2017-08-28T09:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T16:09:53.000Z","uid":62706,"like":180,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfddb7d9652370f944b47aee29e48dc6f3217395","tid":378181,"uid":62706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"尋日星期日朝早5點幾打緊風 橫風橫雨<br />\n我媽咪都要搭的士返工 地點係顯徑嗰頭<br />\n佢老人家大頭蝦又輪盡(50幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n唔知係上落的士定行行下係街跌左部iphone se<br />\n佢發現嗰陣好心急又好想喊 除左我地係唔算有錢部電話對我地來講都幾貴重之外<br />\n部電話同時都係我細妹送俾佢嘅禮物<br />\n佢好珍惜好鍾意 而且入面有佢個孫仔(1歲大)好多生活照同埋我地嘅合照<br />\n諗住已經搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當日下晝居然就有好心人打返來話執到電話 當晚就送返去我媽媽做野間餐廳度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰位好心人仲要不問回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真部電話好新 買左幾個月<br />\n如果賣返出去都有兩三千執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知你有冇上連登 有冇睇到呢個post<br />\n如果你有睇到 或者巴打絲打知度係邊個<br />\n麻煩幫我同佢講聲 好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你令我地知道香港仲有好人<br />\n同時都希望大家以此為榜樣 執到人地財物要俾返人<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df750de951d22aa46495849f25bff0c5ed786855","tid":378181,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申跌過一次手機冇人執返比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84100abfafa8964452560bc6647f721188d9c0a3","tid":378181,"uid":62706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-2